<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٠٠٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6106">مُسْلِمٌ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4340">عَدِيٍّ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3988">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ يَزِيدَ </a>: سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4435">أَبَا مَسْعُودٍ الْبَدْرِيَّ، </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«نَفَقَةُ الرَّجُلِ عَلَى أَهْلِهِ صَدَقَةٌ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>